verbose_text: For the SiO 2 -bound extrudates : the required amounts of ZSM-5 crystals, H 2 O, SiO 2 gel (AEROSIL 300), silica sol (NALCOAG 1034A) and extrusion aid were mixed prior to extrusion into 2 mm diameter extrudates (Al 2 O 3 -bound extrudates were prepared by a similar procedure, using Versal 300).
